Title: Alsisar 40 bed community health center construction


Description: Project involves designing, supervising and collaborating for the construction of

a 40 bed community health center

Traits expectation: Hardworking, willing to learn on site

Expected learning: Knowledge about civil project execution

Specific courses required for project execution: CLEO, NVC
